data.description: Pack your bags. This all brick, low maintenance ranch home is ready to move in. Home features 3 bedrooms, 2 full bath, living room and family room. Kitchen has pantry, oak cabinetry, and stainless appliances. The backyard is amazing with an inground pool that is perfect for entertaining. Located in the popular neighborhood of The Crossing, close to high school and downtown and still have the feel of a rural setting. New HVAC system in 2022.
